On Sullon, the point of pvp is to make other characters camp or leave zone.  PERIOD.  The top guilds, ToW, Hate, and BP <br>
rely on pvp to manipulate the progress of their opponents.<br>
Pvp is very strategy oriented and geared towards controlling access to mobs, planes, or zones.  Also, all TACTICS are considered valid within that strategy.  <br>
