On Vallon, well ..., we have people who believe in an ideal pvp environment, that the game mechanics really do not support.  There are restrictions self-imposed by the server population that limit the range and scope of pvp tactics employed.  Here is where the MB nerf will take its toll.  Tallon too I suppose.<br>
